default1. 2 Th
defaulte issues facing women in STEM careers are not necessarily specific to STEM. Many of the issues apply to women across all careers and are related to work life balance and the consequences of having a family.
default1.3 There are specificities in a career in marine
default STEM that make it even harder for women to succeed compared to ot
defaulther STEM careers. These include
default disproportionately low numbers of women in all roles and the additional challenges of working offshore or at sea.
default1.4 Role models in STEM are vital. These rol
defaulte models must be carefully selected. There is a perception that many of the role models in Marine STEM have got to high level positions by compromising; by not having a family or by becoming “one of the boys” having the opposite effect.
