defaultacademic 
defaultcareers are
default unlikely to offer the same financial rewards as working in industry at a senior level. Depending on the industry you work in,
default&#xa0;
defaultbenefits such as promotion, bonuses, recognition from your client(s), opportunities 
defaultfor CPD 
defaultmay happen in faster timelines than i
defaultn 
defaultacademia. 
defaultWomen 
defaultin particular 
defaultmay feel they want this faster route especially if they are planning to have a break to have a family.
